{"config":{"lang":["en"],"separator":"[\\s\\-]+","pipeline":["stopWordFilter"]},"docs":[{"location":"Apple/macOS/Software/%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85/","title":"\u8f6f\u4ef6\u5b89\u88c5","text":"<p>Applite \u5b98\u7f51\u4e0b\u8f7d\u5730\u5740\uff1a https://aerolite.dev/applite/index.html</p> <p>\u6216\u8005\u901a\u8fc7 Homebrew \u547d\u4ee4\u884c\u5b89\u88c5\uff1a brew install --cask applite</p> <p>Cakebrew \u5b98\u7f51\u4e0b\u8f7d\u5730\u5740\uff1a https://www.cakebrew.com/</p> <p>\u6216\u8005\u901a\u8fc7 Homebrew \u547d\u4ee4\u884c\u5b89\u88c5\uff1a brew install --cask cakebrew</p>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%AD%97%E4%BD%93/","title":"Linux\u5b89\u88c5\u5b57\u4f53","text":""},{"location":"PC/Linux/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%AD%97%E4%BD%93/#_1","title":"\u5c06\u5b57\u4f53\u4fdd\u5b58\u5230\u67d0\u4e2a\u76ee\u5f55","text":"<p>\u4ee5<code>~/LinuxFonts</code>\u4e3a\u4f8b</p>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%AD%97%E4%BD%93/#_2","title":"\u79fb\u52a8","text":"<pre><code>sudo mv ~/LinuxFonts /usr/share/fonts/\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%AD%97%E4%BD%93/#_3","title":"\u5237\u65b0\u7f13\u5b58","text":"<pre><code># yum install mkfontscale\nmkfontscale\nmkfontdir\n# yum install fontconfig\nfc-cache -fv\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/EndeavourOS/Software/Pamac/","title":"Manjaro Pamac on other Arch Linux","text":"<pre><code>yay -S pamac-flatpak\n# yay -S pamac-full\n# yay -S pamac-aur\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/EndeavourOS/Software/VSCodeInsider/","title":"Visual Studio Code Insiders","text":""},{"location":"PC/Linux/EndeavourOS/Software/VSCodeInsider/#install-or-upgrade","title":"Install or Upgrade","text":"<pre><code>yay -S visual-studio-code-insiders-bin\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/EndeavourOS/System/Welcome/","title":"Welcome to EndeavourOS","text":""},{"location":"PC/Linux/EndeavourOS/System/Welcome/#official-welcome-guide","title":"Official Welcome Guide","text":"<pre><code>eos-welcome --enable\n# or\n# eos-welcome --once\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/Manjaro/Software/VMWare/","title":"VMWare","text":""},{"location":"PC/Linux/Manjaro/Software/VMWare/#install-dep","title":"Install Dep","text":"<pre><code>sudo pacman -S fuse2 gtkmm linux-headers pcsclite libcanberra \nyay -S --noconfirm --needed ncurses5-compat-libs\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/Manjaro/Software/VMWare/#install-vmware-workstation","title":"Install VMWare Workstation","text":"<pre><code># yay -S vmware-workstation\nyay -S --noconfirm --needed  vmware-workstation\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/Manjaro/Software/VMWare/#vmmonvmnet","title":"\u63d0\u793avmmon\u6216\u8005vmnet\u6a21\u5757\u6709\u95ee\u9898","text":"<p>\u65b0\u7684\u5185\u6838\u53ef\u80fd\u9700\u8981\u8fd9\u4e2a\u6b65\u9aa4</p> <pre><code>yay -S vmware-host-modules-dkms-git\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/Manjaro/Software/VMWare/#_1","title":"\u542f\u52a8\u670d\u52a1","text":"<pre><code>sudo systemctl enable vmware-networks.service  vmware-usbarbitrator.service\nsudo systemctl start vmware-networks.service  vmware-usbarbitrator.service\n\n# sudo systemctl enable vmware-networks.service  vmware-usbarbitrator.service vmware-hostd.service\n# sudo systemctl start vmware-networks.service  vmware-usbarbitrator.service vmware-hostd.service\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/Manjaro/Software/VMWare/#vmware_1","title":"\u52a0\u8f7dVMware\u6a21\u5757","text":"<pre><code>sudo modprobe -a vmw_vmci vmmon\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/Manjaro/Software/VMWare/#_2","title":"\u542f\u52a8","text":"<pre><code># Launch VMware Workstation Pro:\nvmware\n\n# Launch VMware Workstation Player\nvmplayer\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/Manjaro/Software/VMWare/#ref","title":"Ref","text":"<p>https://segmentfault.com/a/1190000042268631 https://blog.csdn.net/qq_41376740/article/details/121735498 https://cn.linux-console.net/?p=21589</p>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/Manjaro/Software/WPS/","title":"WPS","text":""},{"location":"PC/Linux/Manjaro/Software/WPS/#install","title":"Install","text":"<pre><code>yay -S wps-office-cn wps-office-fonts wps-office-mime-cn\nyay -S wps-office-mui-zh-cn\nyay -S ttf-wps-fonts\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/Manjaro/Software/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E4%B8%8E%E7%BB%B4%E6%8A%A4/flatpak/","title":"flatpak","text":""},{"location":"PC/Linux/Manjaro/Software/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E4%B8%8E%E7%BB%B4%E6%8A%A4/flatpak/#_1","title":"\u66f4\u65b0","text":"<pre><code>flatpak update\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/Manjaro/Software/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E4%B8%8E%E7%BB%B4%E6%8A%A4/pacman/","title":"pacman","text":"<p><code>pacman</code>\u662f<code>Arch Linux</code>\u7684\u5305\u7ba1\u7406\u5668</p>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/Manjaro/Software/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E4%B8%8E%E7%BB%B4%E6%8A%A4/pacman/#ref","title":"Ref","text":"<p>https://ufoseven.github.io/posts/pacman-yay-common-commands/</p>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/Manjaro/Software/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E4%B8%8E%E7%BB%B4%E6%8A%A4/pamac/","title":"pamac\u5de5\u5177","text":"<p><code>pamac</code>\u5de5\u5177\u662f<code>Manjaro</code>\u7cfb\u7edf\u7684\u4e00\u4e2a<code>Arch\u5305\u7ba1\u7406\u5668</code>GUI</p>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/Manjaro/Software/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E4%B8%8E%E7%BB%B4%E6%8A%A4/pamac/#_1","title":"\u652f\u6301","text":"<ul> <li>pacman</li> <li>AUR</li> <li>flatpak</li> </ul>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/Manjaro/Software/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E4%B8%8E%E7%BB%B4%E6%8A%A4/yay/","title":"yay","text":"<p><code>yay</code>\u662f<code>Arch Linux</code>\u7684AUR\u7ba1\u7406\u5668</p>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/Manjaro/Software/%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E6%B3%95/fcitx5/","title":"Fcitx5","text":"<pre><code>sudo pacman -S fcitx5-im fcitx5-chinese-addons fcitx5-material-color fcitx5-configtool\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/Manjaro/Software/%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E6%B3%95/fcitx5/#_1","title":"\u641c\u72d7\u8f93\u5165\u6cd5","text":"<p>\u641c\u72d7\u8f93\u5165\u6cd5\u7684fcitx4\u7248\u672c\u53f7\u4f4d4.2.1\uff0c\u53cd\u6b63\u662f4\u5f00\u5934\u3002 fcitx5\u7248\u672c\u53f7\u76f4\u63a5\u4ece10\u5f00\u5934\u4e86\u3002</p> <pre><code>yay -S fcitx5-sogou fcitx5-pinyin-sougou\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/Manjaro/Software/%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E6%B3%95/fcitx5/#_2","title":"\u6dfb\u52a0\u8f93\u5165\u6cd5","text":"<pre><code>fcitx5-configtool\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/Manjaro/Software/%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E6%B3%95/fcitx5/#ref","title":"Ref","text":"<p>https://www.cnblogs.com/klelee/p/archlinux-fcitx5.html https://forum.ubuntu.com.cn/viewtopic.php?t=494309</p>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/Manjaro/Software/%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E6%B3%95/%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E6%B3%95/","title":"\u8f93\u5165\u6cd5","text":""},{"location":"PC/Linux/Manjaro/Software/%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E6%B3%95/%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E6%B3%95/#wayland","title":"Wayland\u73af\u5883\u53d8\u91cf\u7684\u8bbe\u7f6e","text":"<p>\u7f16\u8f91\u6216\u521b\u5efa<code>~/.fcitx_env.sh</code>\u6587\u4ef6\uff0c\u6dfb\u52a0\u4e0b\u5217\u5185\u5bb9\uff1a</p> <pre><code>export XMODIFIERS=@im=fcitx\nexport GTK_IM_MODULE=fcitx\nexport QT_IM_MODULE=fcitx\nexport SDL_IM_MODULE=fcitx\nexport GLFW_IM_MODULE=fcitx\n</code></pre> <p>\u6700\u597d\u5728<code>~/.bashrc</code>\u548c<code>~/.zshrc</code>\u4e2d\u90fd\u6dfb\u52a0\u4e0b\u9762\u7684\u5185\u5bb9\uff1a</p> <pre><code>source ~/.fcitx_env.sh\n</code></pre> <pre><code>vim ~/.pam_environment\n</code></pre> <pre><code>GTK_IM_MODULE=fcitx\nQT_IM_MODULE=fcitx\nXMODIFIERS=@im=fcitx\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/Manjaro/Software/%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E6%B3%95/%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E6%B3%95/#_2","title":"\u5f00\u673a\u81ea\u542f","text":"<p><code>vim ~/.xinitrc</code></p> <pre><code>fcitx5 &amp;\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/Manjaro/Software/%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E6%B3%95/%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E6%B3%95/#ref","title":"Ref","text":"<p>https://wszqkzqk.github.io/2024/03/09/WPS-Fcitx5/</p>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/Manjaro/System/%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B/","title":"Arch\u8fdc\u7a0b","text":""},{"location":"PC/Linux/Manjaro/System/%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B/#xorg","title":"Xorg","text":""},{"location":"PC/Linux/Manjaro/System/%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B/#rdpxrdp","title":"\u5fae\u8f6fRDP\u534f\u8bae(xrdp)","text":"<p>https://blog.xzr.moe/archives/237/</p>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/Manjaro/System/%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B/#wayland","title":"Wayland","text":""},{"location":"PC/Linux/Manjaro/%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/Chrome%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8AElectron%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E6%B3%95/","title":"Chrome\u4ee5\u53caElectron\u8f93\u5165\u6cd5","text":""},{"location":"PC/Linux/Manjaro/%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/Chrome%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8AElectron%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E6%B3%95/#_1","title":"\u652f\u6301\u7684\u6d4f\u89c8\u5668","text":"<ul> <li>Google Chrome</li> <li>Google Chrome Beta</li> <li>Google Chrome Dev</li> <li>Google Chrome Canary</li> <li>Google Chromium</li> <li>Microsoft Edge</li> <li>Microsoft Edge Beta</li> <li>Microsoft Edge Dev</li> <li>Microsoft Edge Canary</li> </ul>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/Manjaro/%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/Chrome%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8AElectron%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E6%B3%95/#election","title":"\u652f\u6301\u7684Election\u7a0b\u5e8f","text":"<ul> <li>VSCode</li> <li>VSCode-Insiders</li> <li>VSCode-OSS</li> <li>VSCode-OSS-Insiders</li> <li>VSCodium</li> <li>VSCodium-Insiders</li> <li>QQ</li> <li>QQ Music</li> </ul>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/Manjaro/%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/Chrome%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8AElectron%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E6%B3%95/#_2","title":"\u8be6\u7ec6\u6b65\u9aa4(\u50bb\u74dc\u5f0f)","text":""},{"location":"PC/Linux/Manjaro/%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/Chrome%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8AElectron%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E6%B3%95/#ref","title":"Ref","text":"<p>https://fcitx-im.org/wiki/Using_Fcitx_5_on_Wayland#Chromium_.2F_Electron</p>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/Manjaro/%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/Todesk/","title":"Todesk","text":"<p>\u65e0\u6cd5\u767b\u9646(\u65e0\u6cd5\u663e\u793a\u4e8c\u7ef4\u7801)\u4e3a\u6ca1\u6709\u6253\u5f00todesk.service\u6838\u5fc3\u670d\u52a1\u5bfc\u81f4</p> <pre><code>sudo systemctl start todeskd.service\nsudo systemctl enable todeskd.service\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/Manjaro/%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/Todesk/#_1","title":"\u65e0\u5b57","text":"<p>\u7f3a\u5c11noto-fonts-cjk\u5b57\u4f53\u5bfc\u81f4</p> <pre><code>sudo pacman -S noto-fonts-cjk\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/Manjaro/%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/Todesk/#ref","title":"Ref","text":"<p>https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/665192315</p>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/Manjaro/%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1Beta%E7%BC%A9%E6%94%BE/","title":"\u5fae\u4fe1Beta\u7f29\u653e","text":"<p>\u5fae\u4fe1Beta\u91c7\u7528Qt\u6846\u67b6\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u4f7f\u7528Qt\u7684\u65b9\u6cd5\u5373\u53ef\uff01</p>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/Manjaro/%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1Beta%E7%BC%A9%E6%94%BE/#_1","title":"\u65b9\u6cd5","text":"<p>\u8bbe\u7f6e\u73af\u5883\u53d8\u91cf<code>QT_SCALE_FACTOR</code>\u4e3a\u60a8\u559c\u6b22\u7684\u6bd4\u4f8b\u3002</p> <p></p> <p>\u6bd4\u5982\u6211\u5728\u64cd\u4f5c\u7cfb\u7edf\u8bbe\u7f6e\u7684\u6bd4\u4f8b\u4e3a150%\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u53ea\u9700\u8981\u8bbe\u7f6e<code>QT_SCALE_FACTOR=1.5</code>\u5373\u53ef\u3002</p>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/Manjaro/%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1Beta%E7%BC%A9%E6%94%BE/#_2","title":"\u8bbe\u7f6e\u65b9\u6cd5","text":"\u5bf9\u5355\u4e2a\u7a0b\u5e8f\u8bbe\u7f6e\u8bbe\u7f6e\u7cfb\u7edf\u7684\u73af\u5883\u53d8\u91cf <p>\u5982\u679c\u60a8\u4e0d\u5e0c\u671b\u5f71\u54cd\u5176\u4ed6\u7a0b\u5e8f\uff0c\u8bf7\u4fee\u6539<code>.desktop</code>\u6587\u4ef6\u4ee5\u5b9e\u73b0\u4ec5\u5bf9\u5355\u4e2a\u7a0b\u5e8f\u751f\u6548\u3002</p> <p></p> <pre><code>Exec=env QT_SCALE_FACTOR=1.5 wechat-beta %u\n</code></pre> <p>\u5c06\u4e0b\u9762\u7684\u5185\u5bb9\u6dfb\u52a0\u5230<code>~/.bashrc</code>\u6216<code>~/.zshrc</code>\u7b49Shell\u73af\u5883\u7684\u914d\u7f6e\u6587\u4ef6\u4e2d\u3002</p> <pre><code>export QT_SCALE_FACTOR=1.5\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/System/GPU/","title":"Linux\u67e5\u770b\u663e\u5361\u8bbe\u5907\u4fe1\u606f","text":""},{"location":"PC/Linux/System/GPU/#pci-egpu","title":"\u67e5\u770bPCI-E\u4e2d\u7684GPU","text":"<pre><code>lspci | grep -i vga\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/System/GPU/#pci-e","title":"\u67e5\u770b\u6307\u5b9aPCI-E\u8bbe\u5907\u8be6\u60c5","text":""},{"location":"PC/Linux/System/GPU/#ref","title":"Ref","text":"<p>https://blog.csdn.net/conggova/article/details/90202399</p>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/Ubuntu/%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B/","title":"Ubuntu \u8fdc\u7a0b","text":"<p>https://blog.csdn.net/bluewhalerobot/article/details/131575068</p>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/Ubuntu/%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B/#x11","title":"X11","text":""},{"location":"PC/Linux/Ubuntu/%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B/#wayland","title":"Wayland","text":""},{"location":"PC/Linux/Ubuntu/System/DiskMount/","title":"Disk Mount","text":""},{"location":"PC/Linux/Ubuntu/System/DiskMount/#get-uuid","title":"Get UUID","text":"<pre><code>sudo fdisk -l\n\nsudo blkid\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/Ubuntu/System/DiskMount/#ref","title":"Ref","text":"<p>https://help.aliyun.com/zh/ecs/use-cases/configure-uuids-in-the-fstab-file-to-automatically-attach-data-disks https://blog.csdn.net/jiakai82/article/details/107735957</p>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/Ubuntu/System/Kernel/","title":"Ubuntu Linux Kernel","text":""},{"location":"PC/Linux/Ubuntu/System/Kernel/#_1","title":"\u67e5\u770b\u5f53\u524d\u7684\u5185\u6838\u7248\u672c","text":"<pre><code>uname -r\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/Ubuntu/System/Kernel/#_2","title":"\u67e5\u770b\u5f53\u524d\u5df2\u7ecf\u5b89\u88c5\u7684\u5185\u6838","text":"<pre><code>dpkg -l|grep linux-image\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/Ubuntu/System/Kernel/#_3","title":"\u67e5\u8be2\u53ef\u4ee5\u5b89\u88c5\u7684\u5185\u6838\u5217\u8868","text":"<pre><code>sudo apt-cache search linux-image-6.2\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/Ubuntu/System/Kernel/#_4","title":"\u5b89\u88c5\u5185\u6838","text":"<pre><code>sudo apt install -y linux-modules-6.2.0-39-generic\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/Ubuntu/System/Kernel/#ref","title":"Ref","text":"<p>https://blog.csdn.net/u010608421/article/details/115658479</p>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6/GPU/","title":"GPU","text":""},{"location":"PC/Linux/%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6/GPU/#nvtop","title":"nvtop","text":"<pre><code>sudo pacman -S nvtop\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6/GPU/#intel-gpu","title":"Intel GPU","text":"<pre><code>sudo apt install intel-gpu-tools\n</code></pre> <pre><code>sudo pacman -S intel-gpu-tools\n</code></pre> <pre><code>sudo intel_gpu_top\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6/GPU/#amd-gpu","title":"AMD GPU","text":"<pre><code>sudo apt install radeontop\n</code></pre> <pre><code>yay -S radeontop-git\n</code></pre> <pre><code>radeontop\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6/GPU/#nvidia-gpu","title":"NVIDIA GPU","text":"<p>Install NVIDIA Drivers</p> <pre><code>nvidia-smi\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"PC/Linux/%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6/GPU/#ref","title":"Ref","text":"<p>https://github.com/Syllo/nvtop https://blog.csdn.net/jiexijihe945/article/details/135689858 https://cn.linux-terminal.com/?p=6164</p>"},{"location":"PC/Windows/%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E8%B4%A6%E5%8F%B7%E7%99%BB%E5%BD%95%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E5%AF%86%E7%A0%81/","title":"\u5fae\u8f6f\u8d26\u53f7\u767b\u5f55\u7684\u8ba1\u7b97\u673a\u7684\u5bc6\u7801","text":""},{"location":"PC/Windows/%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E8%B4%A6%E5%8F%B7%E7%99%BB%E5%BD%95%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E5%AF%86%E7%A0%81/#windows-11","title":"(Windows 11)\u8ba9\u8ba1\u7b97\u673a\u5b58\u50a8\u5bc6\u7801\u5230\u672c\u673a","text":"<p>\u9996\u5148\u9700\u8981\u5141\u8bb8\u4f7f\u7528\u5bc6\u7801\u767b\u5f55\uff0c</p> <p></p> <p>\u7136\u540e\u6309\u4e0b<code>Win+L</code>\u4f7f\u7528\u5bc6\u7801\u767b\u9646\u4e00\u6b21\u3002</p>"},{"location":"PC/Windows/%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E8%B4%A6%E5%8F%B7%E7%99%BB%E5%BD%95%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E5%AF%86%E7%A0%81/#ref","title":"Ref","text":"<p>https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_52462473/article/details/122657189</p>"},{"location":"PC/Windows/%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6/360%E7%94%BB%E6%8A%A5/","title":"360\u753b\u62a5","text":""},{"location":"PC/Windows/%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6/360%E7%94%BB%E6%8A%A5/#_1","title":"\u76ee\u5f55","text":"<pre><code>C:\\Users\\konghaomin\\AppData\\Roaming\\360huabao\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"PC/Windows/%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6/360%E7%94%BB%E6%8A%A5/#_2","title":"\u6267\u884c\u5378\u8f7d\u7a0b\u5e8f","text":"<p>\u6267\u884c<code>uninstall.exe</code></p>"},{"location":"PC/Windows/%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6/%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E6%A0%A1%E9%AA%8C/","title":"\u6587\u4ef6\u6821\u9a8c","text":""},{"location":"PC/Windows/%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6/%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E6%A0%A1%E9%AA%8C/#_2","title":"\u683c\u5f0f","text":"<pre><code>certutil -hashfile  &lt;\u6587\u4ef6\u540d&gt;  &lt;hash\u7c7b\u578b&gt;\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"PC/Windows/%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6/%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E6%A0%A1%E9%AA%8C/#sha-256","title":"\u83b7\u53d6SHA-256","text":"<pre><code>certutil -hashfile \u6587\u4ef6\u8def\u5f84 sha256\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"PC/Windows/%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6/%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E6%A0%A1%E9%AA%8C/#ref","title":"Ref","text":"<p>https://blog.csdn.net/ThinkAboutLife/article/details/110384620 https://blog.csdn.net/kfepiza/article/details/129152496</p>"},{"location":"PC/Windows/%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6/FreeMind/FreeMind/","title":"FreeMind","text":""},{"location":"PC/Windows/%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6/FreeMind/FreeMind/#ref","title":"Ref","text":"<p>https://blog.csdn.net/lituusliu/article/details/104560698 https://blog.csdn.net/lituusliu/article/details/104560698 https://blog.csdn.net/hansel/article/details/128980132</p>"},{"location":"Server/Hardware/GPU/gpu-burn/","title":"GPU Burn","text":""},{"location":"Server/Hardware/GPU/gpu-burn/#windows","title":"Windows","text":""},{"location":"Server/Hardware/GPU/gpu-burn/#linux","title":"Linux","text":"<p>https://github.com/wilicc/gpu-burn</p> <p>\u9996\u5148\u786e\u8ba4\u6b63\u786e\u5b89\u88c5CUDA\u4ee5\u53ca\u914d\u7f6e\u73af\u5883\u53d8\u91cf\uff0c\u4f7f\u7528<code>nvcc --version</code>\u68c0\u67e5\u3002</p> <pre><code>git clone https://github.com/wilicc/gpu-burn.git\ncd gpu-burn\nmake COMPUTE=&lt;compute capability value&gt;\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"Server/Software/NginX/try_files/","title":"try_files","text":"<p>\u6700\u597d\u628a<code>location /</code>\u653e\u5230\u6700\u540e</p> <pre><code>    location / {\n        root  /usr/share/nginx/web/group-center-dashboard;\n        # index index.html;\n        try_files $uri $uri/ /index.html;\n    }\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"Server/Software/NginX/try_files/#ref","title":"Ref","text":"<p>https://blog.csdn.net/qq_52385631/article/details/123905925 https://cloud.tencent.com/developer/information/NGINX%20-%E5%88%B7%E6%96%B0SPA%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%AD%90%E8%B7%AF%E7%94%B1-salon https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/33379828?from_voters_page=true</p>"},{"location":"Server/System/FreeBSD/FreeBSD%E4%B9%8B%E5%BC%80%E5%90%AFSSH%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1/","title":"FreeBSD\u4e4b\u5f00\u542fSSH\u670d\u52a1","text":""},{"location":"Server/System/FreeBSD/FreeBSD%E4%B9%8B%E5%BC%80%E5%90%AFSSH%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1/#ref","title":"Ref","text":"<p>https://blog.csdn.net/pyf987337461/article/details/116564625</p>"},{"location":"Server/System/FreeBSD/Network/","title":"Network","text":"<p>\u4e5f\u662f\u652f\u6301Linux\u5e38\u7528\u7684<code>ifconfig</code></p>"},{"location":"Server/System/FreeBSD/Network/#ref","title":"Ref","text":"<p>https://blog.csdn.net/zhaojianmingking/article/details/7178276</p> <p>https://docs.freebsd.org/zh-cn/articles/linux-users/#network</p>"},{"location":"Server/System/FreeBSD/OpenVMTools/","title":"Open VM Tools(Run in VMWare)","text":"<pre><code>pkg install open-vmware-tools\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"Server/System/FreeBSD/OpenVMTools/#ref","title":"Ref","text":"<p>https://www.jianshu.com/p/d4e32dbfe1e6</p>"},{"location":"Server/System/FreeBSD/%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A8/","title":"FreeBSD\u5feb\u901f\u5165\u95e8","text":""},{"location":"Server/System/FreeBSD/%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A8/#_1","title":"\u63a8\u8350","text":"<p>https://docs.freebsd.org/zh-cn/articles/linux-users/</p>"},{"location":"Server/System/Linux/VMWare%20Tools/","title":"VMWare Tools","text":""},{"location":"Server/System/Linux/VMWare%20Tools/#windows","title":"Windows","text":"<p>\u95ed\u6e90\u7684\u4e00\u4e2amsi\u5b89\u88c5\u5305</p>"},{"location":"Server/System/Linux/VMWare%20Tools/#linux","title":"Linux","text":"<p>\u73b0\u5728Linux\u63a8\u8350\u4f7f\u7528<code>open-vm-tools</code>\uff0c\u907f\u514dLinux\u5185\u6838\u8f83\u65b0\uff0c\u9700\u8981\u624b\u52a8\u7f16\u8bd1\u3002</p>"},{"location":"Server/System/Linux/VMWare%20Tools/#yum","title":"YUM","text":"<pre><code>yum install -y open-vm-tools\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"Server/System/Linux/VMWare%20Tools/#apt","title":"APT","text":"<pre><code>sudo apt install open-vm*\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"Server/System/Linux/VMWare%20Tools/#ref","title":"Ref","text":""},{"location":"Server/System/Linux/Docker/DockerClean/","title":"Docker Clean","text":""},{"location":"Server/System/Linux/Docker/DockerClean/#prune","title":"prune","text":"<pre><code>docker system prune\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"Server/System/Linux/Docker/DockerClean/#ref","title":"Ref","text":"<p>https://blog.csdn.net/haohaoxuexiyai/article/details/111244328</p>"},{"location":"Server/System/Linux/Docker/DockerOverlay2/","title":"Docker Overlay2 \u76ee\u5f55\u7a7a\u95f4\u5360\u7528\u8fc7\u5927","text":""},{"location":"Server/System/Linux/Docker/DockerOverlay2/#_1","title":"\u4e3b\u8981\u6b65\u9aa4","text":"<ol> <li>\u9010\u7ea7\u67e5\u770b\u5f53\u524d\u76ee\u5f55\u4e0b\u7684\u5404\u76ee\u5f55\u5927\u5c0f</li> </ol> <pre><code>du -sh *\n</code></pre> <p>\u53d1\u73b0\u7f6a\u9b41\u7978\u9996\u4e3aDocker\u7684<code>Overlay2</code>\u76ee\u5f55</p> <ol> <li>\u67e5\u627e\u5927\u4e8e5G\u7684\u6587\u4ef6\u5939</li> </ol> <pre><code>cd /var/lib/docker/overlay2\ndu -h --max-depth=1 --threshold=5G\n</code></pre> <ol> <li>\u67e5\u770b\u8be5\u6587\u4ef6\u5939\u4e0b\u7684\u5404\u76ee\u5f55\u5927\u5c0f</li> </ol> <pre><code>du -sh *\n</code></pre> <p>\u53d1\u73b0\u4e3a<code>tmp</code>\u76ee\u5f55</p> <ol> <li>\u89e3\u51b3\u95ee\u9898</li> </ol> <p>\u5220\u9664tmp\u76ee\u5f55\u4e0b\u7684\u5185\u5bb9(tmp\u4e3a\u4e34\u65f6\u76ee\u5f55)</p>"},{"location":"Server/System/Linux/Docker/DockerOverlay2/#_2","title":"\u53c2\u8003","text":"<p>https://learnku.com/articles/85263</p>"},{"location":"Server/System/Ubuntu/CloseXorg/","title":"Close X.Org","text":""},{"location":"Server/System/Ubuntu/CloseXorg/#gnome","title":"Gnome","text":"<pre><code>sudo systemctl stop gdm3\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"Server/System/Ubuntu/CloseXorg/#kill","title":"Kill","text":"<pre><code>sudo pkill Xorg\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"Server/System/Ubuntu/CloseXorg/#ref","title":"Ref","text":"<p>https://www.jianshu.com/p/36dcf5185f01</p>"},{"location":"Server/System/Ubuntu/RedirectPort/","title":"Redirect Port","text":""},{"location":"Server/System/Ubuntu/RedirectPort/#iptables","title":"<code>iptables</code>","text":""},{"location":"Server/System/Ubuntu/RedirectPort/#ref","title":"Ref","text":"<p>https://www.cnblogs.com/wanglouxiaozi/p/18121493</p>"},{"location":"Server/System/WSL/AMDRocM/","title":"AMD RocM WSL","text":""},{"location":"Server/System/WSL/AMDRocM/#install","title":"Install","text":"<p>https://rocm.docs.amd.com/projects/radeon/en/latest/docs/install/wsl/install-radeon.html</p>"},{"location":"Server/System/WSL/AMDRocM/#install-pytorch","title":"Install PyTorch","text":"<pre><code>pip install torch torchvision torchaudio --index-url https://download.pytorch.org/whl/rocm6.1\n</code></pre> <p>https://rocm.docs.amd.com/projects/radeon/en/latest/docs/install/wsl/install-pytorch.html</p>"},{"location":"Server/System/WSL/AMDRocM/#pytorch-support-wsl","title":"PyTorch Support WSL","text":"<pre><code>location=`pip show torch | grep Location | awk -F \": \" '{print $2}'`\ncd ${location}/torch/lib/\nrm libhsa-runtime64.so*\ncp /opt/rocm/lib/libhsa-runtime64.so.1.2 libhsa-runtime64.so\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"Server/System/WSL/AMDRocM/#glibcxx","title":"GLIBCXX","text":"<pre><code>strings /usr/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libstdc++.so.6 | grep GLIBCXX\n\ncd /home/cedric/anaconda3/envs/decdiff_env/bin/../lib/\nmv libstdc++.so.6 libstdc++.so.6.old\nln -s /usr/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libstdc++.so.6 libstdc++.so.6\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"Server/System/WSL/AMDRocM/#ref","title":"Ref","text":"<p>https://rocm.docs.amd.com/projects/radeon/en/latest/docs/install/wsl/install-radeon.html https://rocm.docs.amd.com/projects/radeon/en/latest/docs/install/wsl/install-pytorch.html https://pytorch.org/get-started/locally/ https://blog.csdn.net/CCCDeric/article/details/129292944</p>"},{"location":"Server/System/WSL/ConnectHost/","title":"WSL\u8054\u4e0d\u901a\u5bbf\u4e3b\u673a","text":""},{"location":"Server/System/WSL/ConnectHost/#1-ipconfigwsl","title":"\u6b65\u9aa41: ipconfig\u67e5\u770bWSL\u865a\u62df\u7f51\u5361\u540d\u79f0","text":"<pre><code>ipconfig\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"Server/System/WSL/ConnectHost/#2","title":"\u6b65\u9aa42: \u6dfb\u52a0\u9632\u706b\u5899\u89c4\u5219","text":"<pre><code>New-NetFirewallRule -DisplayName \"WSL\" -Direction Inbound  -InterfaceAlias \"vEthernet (WSL)\" -Action Allow\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"Server/System/WSL/ConnectHost/#ref","title":"Ref","text":"<p>https://blog.csdn.net/Cypher_X/article/details/123011200</p>"},{"location":"Server/System/WSL/NetworkMode/","title":"Network Mode","text":"<p><code>~/.wslconfig</code></p> <pre><code>[experimental]\nautoMemoryReclaim=gradual  \nnetworkingMode=mirrored\ndnsTunneling=true\nfirewall=true\nautoProxy=true\n</code></pre> <p>networkingMode \u4e3amirrored \u8868\u793a\u7f51\u7edc\u6a21\u5f0f\u4f7f\u7528\u955c\u50cf\u6a21\u5f0f\uff0c\u4f1a\u955c\u50cf\u5bbf\u4e3b\u673a\u7684\u7f51\u7edc\u8bbe\u7f6e\uff0c\u80fd\u66f4\u597d\u7684\u96c6\u6210\u5bbf\u4e3b\u673a\u548cWSL\u7684\u7f51\u7edc\u3002</p> <p>autoProxy \u5f00\u542f\u4e86\u81ea\u52a8\u4ee3\u7406\u7684\u529f\u80fd\uff0c\u610f\u5473 WSL \u81ea\u52a8\u914d\u7f6e\u4ee3\u7406\u8bbe\u7f6e\u3002</p> <p><code>wsl --shutdown</code></p>"},{"location":"Server/System/WSL/NetworkMode/#ref","title":"Ref","text":"<p>https://overstarry.vip/posts/wsl_error1/ https://blog.csdn.net/m0_57830768/article/details/137495770</p>"},{"location":"Server/System/WSL/RedirectPort/","title":"WSL2\u7aef\u53e3\u8f6c\u53d1","text":""},{"location":"Server/System/WSL/RedirectPort/#_1","title":"\u81ea\u52a8\u8f6c\u53d1","text":"<p>\u5728WINDOWS\u7528\u6237\u76ee\u5f55\u4e0b\u521b\u5efa\u4e00\u4e2a\u6587\u4ef6</p> <p>.wslconfig</p> <pre><code>[wsl2]\nlocalhostForwarding=true\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"Server/System/WSL/RedirectPort/#vscode","title":"\u501f\u52a9VSCode","text":""},{"location":"Server/System/WSL/RedirectPort/#ref","title":"Ref","text":"<p>https://blog.csdn.net/xuankucom/article/details/132923686</p>"},{"location":"Server/System/Windows%20Server/RDP/","title":"RDP","text":""},{"location":"Server/System/Windows%20Server/RDP/#rdp-enhence","title":"RDP Enhence","text":"<p>https://github.com/stascorp/rdpwrap</p>"},{"location":"Server/System/Windows%20Server/RDP/#rdpwrapini","title":"rdpwrap.ini\u7684\u66f4\u65b0","text":"<p>https://github.com/affinityv/INI-RDPWRAP/blob/master/rdpwrap.ini</p> <p>https://blog.csdn.net/ty0_0/article/details/114862541 https://blog.csdn.net/u010804317/article/details/104011926</p>"},{"location":"Server/System/Windows%20Server/RDP/#rdp-multi-user-connection","title":"RDP Multi-User Connection","text":"<p>https://post.smzdm.com/p/aeked05z/</p> <p>https://www.cnblogs.com/heardic/p/14012001.html https://www.cnblogs.com/hyyx/p/15207866.html https://www.cnblogs.com/hyyx/p/15149135.html https://blog.csdn.net/beyondqd/article/details/8524313 https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_46031767/article/details/122937892</p> <p>https://blog.csdn.net/gtj0617/article/details/136551002</p>"},{"location":"Server/System/Windows%20Server/RDP/#rdp-windows-defender-firewall","title":"RDP Windows Defender Firewall","text":"<p>https://blog.csdn.net/michaelehome/article/details/79555799</p>"},{"location":"Server/System/Windows%20Server/RDP/#multi-user-open-rdp","title":"Multi-User Open RDP","text":"<p>https://blog.csdn.net/m0_49113674/article/details/109908233</p>"},{"location":"Server/System/Windows%20Server/RDP/#webvpn","title":"WebVpn","text":"<p>\u5982\u679c\u5b66\u6821\u7684\u7f51\u9875\u7248WebVpn\u65e0\u6cd5\u8fde\u63a5\uff0c\u9700\u8981\u4f7f\u7528<code>RDPWrap</code>\u5c06<code>Authentication Mode</code>\u9009\u62e9\u4e3a<code>GUI Authentication Only</code>\u3002</p> <p></p>"},{"location":"Server/System/Windows%20Server/Network/NetWorkProfile/","title":"Windows Network Profile","text":""},{"location":"Server/System/Windows%20Server/Network/NetWorkProfile/#get-network-profile","title":"Get Network Profile","text":"<pre><code>Get-NetConnectionProfile\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"Server/System/Windows%20Server/Network/NetWorkProfile/#set-network-profile","title":"Set Network Profile","text":"<pre><code>Set-NetConnectionProfile -Name \"&lt;NetworkName&gt;\" -NetworkCategory Private\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"Server/System/Windows%20Server/Network/NetWorkProfile/#ref","title":"Ref","text":"<p>https://www.anyviewer.cn/how-to/change-network-from-public-to-private-2111.html</p>"}]}